column1: As a user, Order Id should not accept all zero values in the field
column26:
Steps to Reproduce

# Go to the Application
# Go to login and Go to Product returns
# Go to the Products fields
# Go to Order Id
# Verify whether Order Id accepts all zeros values in the field

Expected Result

Order Id should not accept all zeroes values 



Actual result

It accepts zero value
